---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About - Guiding Point Consulting"
  description="I help teams modernize their web presence and build AI-enabled content operations—without losing the human element."
>
  <!-- Hero with Parallax -->
  <section class="about-hero parallax-section">
    <div class="parallax-bg" data-speed="0.5">
      <div class="gradient-orb orb-1"></div>
      <div class="gradient-orb orb-2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p class="hero-text">
        We help teams modernize their web presence and build AI-enabled content operations without losing the human element that makes communication work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-section">
        <p class="large-text">
          Oue strength is being the liaison between leadership and technical teams. We translate goals into systems, roadmaps, and execution plans that teams can actually ship. The result is a website and content process that feels clear, consistent, and measurable.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>What you can expect</h2>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Clear scope and transparent communication</li>
            <li>Human-centered UX and messaging</li>
            <li>Systems thinking (not just pages)</li>
            <li>Practical AI workflows with quality controls</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>Tools & strengths</h2>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Web strategy, IA, and content structure</li>
            <li>Performance-first builds and clean handoffs</li>
            <li>SEO and measurement foundations</li>
            <li>AI content operations (SOPs, prompts, governance)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Approach Section -->
  <section class="approach-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="approach-content">
        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <div class="approach-grid">
          <div class="approach-item">
            <div class="approach-number">1</div>
            <h3>Listen First</h3>
            <p>We start by understanding your goals, constraints, and team dynamics before proposing solutions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="approach-item">
            <div class="approach-number">2</div>
            <h3>Systems Thinking</h3>
            <p>Every recommendation considers how it fits into your broader workflow and long-term goals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="approach-item">
            <div class="approach-number">3</div>
            <h3>Ship & Iterate</h3>
            <p>We prioritize getting something working quickly, then improving it based on real feedback and data.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Let's work together</h2>
        <p>Ready to modernize your website and content operations? Let's start with a conversation.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Parallax Hero */
  .parallax-section {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  min-height: auto;  /* Remove fixed height */
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);  /* Less padding */
}

  .parallax-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: -50%;
    z-index: 0;
    will-change: transform;
  }

  .gradient-orb {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(100px);
    opacity: 0.5;
    animation: float 15s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .orb-1 {
    width: 700px;
    height: 700px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #ac3430 20%, #ff6b6b 40%, transparent 70%);
    top: -150px;
    left: -150px;
    z-index: 0;
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }

  .orb-2 {
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #dcceaa 20%, #f5e6c8 40%, transparent 70%);
    top: 50px;
    right: -100px;
    z-index: 0;
    animation-delay: -7s;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
    }
    25% {
      transform: translate(30px, -30px) scale(1.05);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.95);
    }
    75% {
      transform: translate(20px, 30px) scale(1.02);
    }
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hero-text {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--gray-700);
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
  }

  .content-section {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .large-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray-700);
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .check-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .check-list li {
    padding-left: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    position: relative;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .check-list li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--rust);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .approach-section {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    background: var(--gray-50);
  }

  .approach-content {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .approach-content h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  .approach-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .approach-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
  }

  .approach-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: var(--rust);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .approach-item h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .approach-item p {
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-text {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .approach-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .gradient-orb {
      width: 350px;
      height: 350px;
    }

    .parallax-section {
      min-height: auto;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    const scrolled = window.pageYOffset;
    const parallaxBg = document.querySelector('.parallax-bg') as HTMLElement;
    
    if (parallaxBg && scrolled < window.innerHeight) {
      parallaxBg.style.transform = `translateY(${scrolled * 0.5}px)`;
    }
  });
</script>